<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>LuvTheTask - Home</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel = "stylesheet" type = "text/css" href = "/stylesheets/homepage.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="floating-elements">
    </div>
    
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <div class="brand">
                <div class="brand-logo">
                    <i class="fas fa-heart"></i>
                </div>
                <h1 class="brand-name">LuvTheTask</h1>
            </div>
            
            <div class="nav-buttons">
                <button class="btn btn-primary">
                    <a href = "/login">
                    <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt"></i> Login
                    </a>
                </button>
                <button class="btn btn-secondary">
                    <a href = "/register">
                    <i class="fas fa-user-plus"></i> Register
                    </a>
                </button>
                <button class="btn btn-outline">
                    <a href = "/profile">
                    <i class="fas fa-user"></i> Profile
                    </a>
                </button>
                <button class="btn btn-outline">
                    <a href = "/task">
                    <i class="fas fa-plus-circle"></i> Create Task
                    </a>
                </button>
            </div>
        </header>
        
        <section class="hero">
            <h1>Organize Your Life, One Task at a Time</h1>
            <p>LuvTheTask is your personal task management companion that helps you stay organized, focused, and productive. Add tasks as they come to mind, track your progress, and celebrate your accomplishments by deleting completed tasks.</p>
            <p>With our intuitive interface and powerful features, managing your daily responsibilities has never been easier or more enjoyable.</p>
            
            <div class="features">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-plus"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Add Tasks</h3>
                    <p>Easily add new tasks with our simple creation form. Set priorities, due dates, and categories to keep everything organized.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Track Progress</h3>
                    <p>Monitor your task completion with visual progress indicators. Watch your productivity grow as you check off completed items.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-trash-alt"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Delete Completed</h3>
                    <p>Experience the satisfaction of deleting tasks you've completed. Clear your list and make space for new accomplishments.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
    <script src = "/javascripts/homepage.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
